platform.description: Fuafuaga o le Faʻataʻitaʻiga o Tupe Tumuai (ICO) ma le tuʻufaʻatasiga o le KYC, faʻatulagaina o konekarate atamai, ma le usitaʻia o tulafono.
platform.title: Fa'atau Tupe Fa'ailoga

transfers.description: Puleaina fa'aliliu tupe totino i totonu o teugatupe ma fa'agasologa fa'atagaina ma siakiina fa'amanatuga.
transfers.title: Feaveai I Totonu

durations.description: Fa'avasega taimi teu tupe, taimi matua, ma fa'atatauina o tama'i tuputupu mo oloa eseese.
durations.title: Umi o Tupe Fa'aalu

extensions.description: oloa teu tupe mamafa ma ta'iala fa'apitoa AI, auaunaga fa'amau, ma lātou fa'ailoga faila.
extensions.title: oloa Tupe Fa'aalu

history.description: Fa'ata'ita'iga fa'atinoga teu tupe atoatoa ma su'esu'eina ROI ma malamalama puleaina ata tupe.
history.title: Su'esu'ega Tupe Fa'aalu

management.description: Puleaina oloa teu tupe ma foafoaga o fuafuaga, su'esu'eina fa'atinoga, ma meafaigaluega va'aiga ata tupe.
management.title: Puleaina Tupe Fa'aalu

plans.description: Fatu ma puleaina oloa teu tupe ma ata lamatiaga, fa'atatauina o tupe maua, ma fa'avasegaina taimi.
plans.title: Fuafuaga Tupe Fa'aalu

base.description: Faiga puleaina malamalama atoatoa ma su'esue'ina fa'apitoa AI ma fa'aleleia anotusi.
base.title: Faletusi o Malamalama

applications.description: Iloilo ma fa'agasologa talosaga Iloa Lau Tagata Fa'atau ma fa'amaoniaga pepa, iloiloga lamatiaga, ma fa'agasologa fa'atagaina.
applications.title: Talosaga KYC

levels.description: Fa'avasega fa'amaoni fa'amaoniaga ma mana'oga fa'apitoa, tapula'a, ma avanoa avanoa mo vaega tagata fa'aoga eseese.
levels.title: Tulaga Fa'amaoni

tools.description: Meafaigaluega tausia faiga e aofia ai fa'aleleia fa'amaumauga, puleaina fa'aputuga mea, ma meafaigaluega fe'avea'i.
tools.title: Meafaigaluega Tausiga

extensions.description: Lātou pisinisi fa'atau ma maketi numera ma meafaigaluega atoatoa fa'atau ma puipuiga fa'atau.
extensions.title: Fofo o Maketi

wallets.description: Puleaina ātō tupe matua tulaga pisinisi mamafa ma puipuiga saini tele ma fa'afesoota'iga teuina mālūlū.
wallets.title: Ato Tupe Matua

library.description: Puleaina fa'asalalauga sagatotonu ma teuina ao, fa'aleleia ata, ma fa'afesoota'iga CDN mo fa'atinoga sili ona lelei.
library.title: Faletusi Ata ma Leo

marketplace.description: Maketi NFT polofesa ma meafaigaluega fai, puleaina totogi fa'ausiusita'i, ma gafatia faleoloa.
marketplace.title: Maketi NFT

templates.description: Mamanu fa'ailoga fa'apitoa ma tu'uina atu auala tele ma fesuiaiga fa'apitoa.
templates.title: Faʻataʻitaʻiga Faʻailoaga

management.description: Fa'atinoina fa'atasi o fa'agasologa fa'atau ma le puleaina i luga o fa'avae fefa'ataua'iga uma ma vasega o aseta.
management.title: Puleaina Fa'atonuga

platform.description: Fuafuaga fefaʻatauaʻi tagata-i-tagata ma auaunaga escrow, foʻia o feʻesaʻaiga, ma le lagolago o faitotoʻa totogi tele.
platform.title: Fefa'ataua'iga P2P

gateways.description: Fa'atulagaina ma mata'ituina faitoto'a totogi ma su'esu'ega fa'a-fa'asese, siaki fa'atulafonoina, ma su'esu'ega fa'atinoga.
gateways.title: Faitoto'a Totogi

methods.description: Puleaina filifiliga totogi avanoa e aofia ai kata, fa'aliliuga faletupe, teutupe-tama'i numera, ma totogi cryptocurrency.
methods.title: Auala Totogi

systems.description: Puleaina atoatoa o fa'avae totogi e aofia ai faitoto'a, metotia, ma mata'ituina fa'agasologa fefa'ataua'iga.
systems.title: Faiga Totogi

extensions.description: Faʻaopoopoga o fuafuaga maualuga e tuʻuina atu galuega faʻapitoa mo fefaʻatauaʻiga, maketi, ma taʻitaʻiga pisinisi.
extensions.title: Fa'alauteleina

settings.description: Faʻatulagaga autu o le fuafuaga e aofia ai le faʻailoga, faʻalelalolagi, faiga puipuiga, ma fesuiaiga o foliga.
settings.title: Fa'atulagaga Fa'avae

tasks.description: Fa'atulagaga fa'aautomatika o galuega ma mata'ituina galuega, taulimaina o le fua, ma fa'aleleia fa'atinoga.
tasks.title: Galuega Fuafuaina

orders.description: Puleaina fa'atonuga fefa'ataua'iga vave ma mata'ituina fa'atinoina taimi-moni ma su'esu'ega a'afiaga o le maketi.
orders.title: Fa'atonuga Vave

platform.description: Fuafuaga staking atoatoa ma le puleaina o tagata faʻamaonia, tufatufaina o taui, ma le puipuiga mai le taia.
platform.title: Auaunaga Staking

administration.description: Suite puleaina fa'asologa atoatoa mo le fa'atulagaga fa'avae, mata'ituina, ma fa'agasologa tausia.
administration.title: Faiga

announcements.description: Faiga fa'asalalau lautele o le fa'avae ma le fa'atulagaga, fa'atatauina, ma gafatia siaki fa'afeiloa'iga.
announcements.title: Faʻasalalauga Faiga

logs.description: Faiga fa'amaumauga fa'atasi ma mata'ituina taimi-moni, fa'aputuina fa'amaumauga, ma gafatia su'esu'ega fa'aonaponei.
logs.title: Faʻamaumauga Faiga

updates.description: Fa'afouina fa'aautomatika o le faiga ma gafatia toe-fa'afo'i, fa'apipi'i puipuiga saogalemu, ma puleaina tautua vala.
updates.title: Faʻafouga Faiga

management.description: Puleaina atoatoa o le soifua o le token ma gafatia faia, mu, ma pule.
management.title: Puleaina Tama'i Tupe

extensions.description: Fa'avae fefa'ataua'iga fa'apitoa ma ituaiga fa'atonuga fa'aonaponei, meafaigaluega su'esu'ega maketi, ma fa'atinoina tulaga fa'alapotopotoga.
extensions.title: Fa'avae Fefa'ataua'iga Pisinisi

infrastructure.description: Puleaina fa'avae fefa'ataua'iga e aofia ai saini fefa'ataua'iga, fa'atulagaga maketi, ma faiga fa'agasologa fa'atonuga.
infrastructure.title: Fa'avae Fefa'ataua'iga

logs.description: Tala fa'asologa fefa'ataua'iga atoatoa ma fa'amasinoga fa'aonaponei, gafatia fa'aalu ese, ma ala siaki.
logs.title: Fa'amaumauga Fefa'ataua'iga

management.description: Mata'ituina atoatoa o fefa'ataua'iga ma fa'amaumauga fa'apitoa, fa'amasinoina, ma gafatia puleaina fa'aliliuga.
management.title: Puleaina Fefa'ataua'iga

management.description: Puleaina atoatoa o le tausaga o tagata faʻaoga e aofia ai le resitala, faʻamaoniaga, tofiina o matafaioi, ma mea faigaluega fesoʻotaʻiga ma tagata faʻatau mo le puleaina atoatoa o tagata faʻaoga.
management.title: Tagata Fa'aoga

tracking.description: Puleaina UTXO fa'aonaponei ma su'esu'ega kalafi fefa'ataua'iga ma uiga fa'atūlaga-tūlaga.
tracking.title: Siaki UTXO

management.description: Puleaina teugatupe tupe-eseese ma mata'ituina paleni, pulea saogalemu, ma puleaina fa'aputuga.
management.title: Puleaina Ato Tupe

logs.description: Mata'ituina talosaga to'ese tupe ma siakiina tulaga, fa'agasologa fa'amaoniga, ma fa'amaoniga fa'atulafonoina.
logs.title: Fa'amaumauga Tupe To'ese

management.description: Puleaina atoatoa o le faiga to'ese tupe ma fa'agasologa fa'aautomatika, puipuiga fa'asese, ma pulea fa'atulafonoina.
management.title: Puleaina Tupe To'ese

methods.description: Fa'atulagaina filifiliga to'ese tupe e aofia ai fa'aliliuga faletupe, to'ese crypto, ma fa'agaioiga vaega-tolu.
methods.title: Auala Tupe To'ese

trading.title: Fefaauigaaga
trading.description: Maua le avanoa i tulaga fefaauigaaga atoatoa ma meafaigaluega faailoga maualuluga, faamatalaga o maketi i taimi nei, ma mea e mafai ona faaaogaina tulaga taulaga mo ituaiga oloa uma.

spot.title: Fefaauigaaga Vave
spot.description: Faia poloaiga faatau ma faatau vave i tau o le maketi i le taimi nei ma ituaiga poloaiga maualuluga, siata loloto, ma meafaigaluega fefaauigaaga taulaga.

binary.title: Filifiliga Lua
binary.description: Fefaauigaaga filifiliga lua ma su'esu'ega fa'apitoa, meafaigaluega fa'atautaia lamatiaga, ma fa'atinoina fa'afaigofie mo ta'iala e fa'aoga ai le taimi.

forex.title: Fefaauigaaga Tupe
forex.description: Avanoa i maketi fefaauigaaga tupe a le lalolagi ma le tu'ufa'atasiga o le MetaTrader 4/5, siata maualuluga, ma le fa'atinoina o le tulaga fa'alapotopotoga.

p2p.title: Fefaauigaaga P2P
p2p.description: Auai i fefaauigaaga cryptocurrency saogalemu a tagata ta'ito'atasi ma le puipuiga escrow, auala totogi fetuutuunai, ma tau tauva.

portfolio.title: Pusa Tupe
portfolio.description: Fa'atulagaga Portfolio atoatoa mo le su'esu'eina o aseta, su'esu'eina o fa'atinoga, ma pulea au meafaigaluega tau tupe i luga o tulaga uma.

wallet.title: Pulea Teutupe
wallet.description: Teutupe tupe eseese saogalemu ma le su'esu'eina o paleni i taimi nei, tala o fefaauigaaga, ma le mafai ona teu/ave tupe fa'afaigofie.

transactions.title: Tala o Fefaauigaaga
transactions.description: Faamaumauga auiliili o fefaauigaaga ma le fa'aogaina maualuga, mea e mafai ona auina atu, ma ala auditaga atoatoa mo gaoioiga tau tupe uma.

transfers.title: Fesiitaiga
transfers.description: Auaunaga fesiitai i totonu ma fafo ma le gaoioina vave, totogi tauva, ma le lagolago o tupe eseese.

investments.title: Tupe Teufaafaigaluega
investments.description: Avanoa tupe teufaafaigaluega eseese ma su'esu'ega tulaga taulaga, meafaigaluega iloiloina lamatiaga, ma le su'esu'eina o fa'atinoga i ituaiga aseta eseese.

plans.title: Fuafuaga Tupe Teufaafaigaluega
plans.description: Ta'iala tupe teufaafaigaluega fa'atulagaina ma fa'amatalaga loloto o lamatiaga, fa'amaumauga fa'atinoga o le tala fa'asolopito, ma tu'utu'uga fetuutuunai e fetaui ma au sini tau tupe.

staking.title: Taui Staking
staking.description: Maua tupe maua le aunoa ma le galue e ala i le staking cryptocurrency ma fua APY tauva, vaitaimi loka fetuutuunai, ma le tufatufaina otometi o taui.

ico.title: Fa'atauga Togi
ico.description: Avanoa vave i Fa'atauga Tupe Muamua (ICO) ua su'esu'eina ma lipoti su'esu'ega atoatoa, su'esu'ega o tokenomics, ma siaki tupe teufaafaigaluega.

marketplace.title: Maketi
marketplace.description: Su'esu'e maketi fa'aeletoroni ma feso'ota'iga lelei ma fefa'ataua'iga saogalemu, tagata fa'atau fa'amaonia, ma puipuiga atoatoa o tagata fa'atau.

nft.title: Fale Fa'aali NFT
nft.description: Su'esu'e, fatu, ma fefa'ataua'i aseta fa'aeletoroni tulaga ese i la matou maketi NFT filifilia ma gafatia fa'aliliu ma totogi o tagata fatu.

store.title: Faleoloa
store.description: Maketi maualuga o lo'o fa'aalia oloa fa'aeletoroni ma feso'ota'iga ma fa'agasologa o totogi saogalemu, fe'avea'i i le lalolagi atoa, ma puipuiga o tagata fa'atau.

services.title: Auaunaga
services.description: Auaunaga fa'apolofesa ma meafaigaluega e fa'aleleia ai lou fa'ata'ita'iga fefa'ataua'iga, e aofia ai polokalame fa'atau, fa'apogai a'oa'oga, ma lagolago maualuga.

affiliate.title: Polokalame Fa'atau
affiliate.description: Fa'atupega le tele o au feso'ota'iga e ala i la matou polokalame fa'atau atoatoa ma totogi fa'atauva lelei, siaki i taimi moni, ma meafaigaluega fa'asalalauga.

support.title: Nofoaga Lagolago
support.description: Lagolago fa'atau fa'apolofesa ma puleaina o pepa, gafatia talanoa ola, ma puleaina fa'apitoa o tala mo tagata fa'aoga maualuga.

faq.title: Fa'amaumauga Malamalama
faq.description: Fa'amaumauga atoatoa, fa'amatalaga, ma fesili masani e fesoasoani ia te oe e fa'aogaina lelei gafatia o le fa'avae.

insights.title: Malamalama
insights.description: Su'esu'ega maketi fa'apolofesa, malamalama fefa'ataua'iga, ma tala fatu mai la matou 'au faufautua tupe ma tagata su'esu'e maketi.
